                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "LEG 1 FLAG: React controlled-select desync — DOM .value sets but onChange state reverts to Please Select; required Property Type empty -> submit blocked, no row. Fix path: _valueTracker.setValue reset before change event, OR direct POST to submit endpoint. Possible doc-upload gate too."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
